# GenUI Service 扩展注册示例
# 用法:先启动服务(mvn -pl examples/genui-service spring-boot:run),
#      然后用 IDE 的 HTTP Client(IntelliJ/VS Code REST Client)逐条执行,
#      或复制末尾的 curl 等价命令。
#
# 注意:注册不持久化——服务重启后此注册丢失,调用方应在自身启动时重注册
#      (PUT 替换语义保证幂等)。

### 1. 查看当前已注册的 Generation Context(应含三套预制种子)
GET http://localhost:3001/v1/contexts

### 2. 注册一个下游业务扩展:自定义组件 + 工具
#    组件名不得与 base contract(Stack/Table/...)碰撞,否则 409。
#    提示:自定义组件要在 demo 前端渲染,需要前端侧 dslLibrary.extend() 配套注册;
#    仅后端注册时,组件只进入 prompt 契约(模型可见),前端无法渲染。
PUT http://localhost:3001/v1/contexts/team-a-billing
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "components": {
    "BillingCard": {
      "signature": "BillingCard(title: string, amount: number, currency?: \"CNY\" | \"USD\")",
      "description": "账单卡片:展示账期金额,currency 默认 CNY。"
    }
  },
  "componentGroups": [
    {
      "name": "Billing",
      "components": ["BillingCard"],
      "notes": ["账单场景优先使用 BillingCard 而非通用 Card。"]
    }
  ],
  "tools": [
    {
      "name": "queryBill",
      "description": "按账期查询账单明细",
      "inputSchema": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "period": { "type": "string" }
        },
        "required": ["period"]
      },
      "annotations": { "readOnlyHint": true }
    }
  ],
  "additionalRules": [
    "金额一律保留两位小数。"
  ]
}

### 3. 验证注册生效:列表应出现 team-a-billing
GET http://localhost:3001/v1/contexts

### 4. 验证拼装生效:prompt 中应包含 BillingCard 与 queryBill
POST http://localhost:3001/v1/prompts/assemble
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contextId": "team-a-billing"
}

### 5. 重复注册 = 整体替换(幂等);版本升到 1.1.0
PUT http://localhost:3001/v1/contexts/team-a-billing
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "version": "1.1.0",
  "components": {
    "BillingCard": {
      "signature": "BillingCard(title: string, amount: number, currency?: \"CNY\" | \"USD\" | \"EUR\")",
      "description": "账单卡片:展示账期金额,currency 默认 CNY。"
    }
  }
}

### 6. 名称碰撞示例:Stack 是 base contract 组件,预期 409
PUT http://localhost:3001/v1/contexts/bad-ext
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "components": {
    "Stack": { "signature": "Stack()", "description": "试图覆盖基础组件" }
  }
}

# ---- curl 等价命令(任选) ----
# curl http://localhost:3001/v1/contexts
# curl -X PUT http://localhost:3001/v1/contexts/team-a-billing \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -d '{"version":"1.0.0","components":{"BillingCard":{"signature":"BillingCard(title: string, amount: number)","description":"账单卡片"}}}'
# curl -X POST http://localhost:3001/v1/prompts/assemble \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"contextId":"team-a-billing"}'
